---
import { Image, Picture } from '@astrojs/image/components';
import headshot from '@assets/headshot.png';
import PageLayout from '@layouts/page.astro';

import ButtonBar from '@components/buttonbar.astro';
import ButtonLink from '@components/buttonlink.astro';
import Container from '@components/container.astro';
import Head from '@components/head.astro';
import Navbar from '@components/navbar.astro';
import Socials from '@components/socials.astro';

const title = "About";
const description = "I\'m Anna Hsu (she/her), a Taiwanese-American gal studying Computer Engineering and Computer Science at the University of Southern California.";
const permalink = "/about";
---

<PageLayout>

  <head>

    <Head {title} {description} {permalink} />
    <style lang="scss">
      .content {
        flex: 999 1 300px;
      }

      .tangent {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 64px;
      }

      .sidebar {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 32px;
        flex: 1 1 0;
      }

      .wrap {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
      }

      .rectangle-wrap {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: -1;
      }

      .rectangle {
        background: var(--light);
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 50;
        animation: whee 1s ease forwards;
      }

      .headshot {
        z-index: 100;
        max-width: 300px;
        max-height: 300px;
        animation: photo 1s ease forwards;
      }

      @media (max-width: 374px) {
        .headshot {
          max-width: 200px;
          max-height: 200px;
        }
      }

      .bar {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .rectangle {
          animation: none;
          transform: rotate(6deg);
          box-shadow: var(--cutout);
        }
      }

      @keyframes photo {
        100% {
          box-shadow: var(--cutout);
        }
      }

      @keyframes whee {
        0% {
          opacity: 0%;
          transform: rotate(0deg);
        }

        100% {
          transform: rotate(6deg);
          box-shadow: var(--cutout);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <Navbar />
    <Container>
      <h1>Whomst?</h1>
      <div class="tangent">
        <div class="sidebar">
          <div class="wrap">
            <div class="rectangle-wrap">
              <div class="rectangle" />
            </div>
            <div class="headshot">
              <Picture src={headshot} widths={[400, 800]} sizes="(max-width: 374px) 200px, (min-width: 375px) 300px" alt="Anna Hsu headshot" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bar">
            <ButtonBar>
              <ButtonLink href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BX_bHZ3Q3J8osZ8oj2nemc0Enos3d6Vj/view?usp=sharing">
                Resume</ButtonLink>
              <ButtonLink href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/10_ho2LngZB7iuxkERGgJ1l3kF9orc3sH/view?usp=sharing">
                Headshot</ButtonLink>
            </ButtonBar>
            <Socials />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Hallo! My name is Anna (she/her) and I'm a Taiwanese-American gal studying Computer Engineering and
            Computer Science at the <a href="https://usc.edu">University of Southern California</a>. I'm originally from
            Northern Virginia and I graduated from <a href="https://tjhsst.fcps.edu">Thomas Jefferson High School for
              Science and Technology</a>. That's where I discovered my love for designing impactful products and sharing
            stories that go untold.</p>
          <p>At SC, I'm part of <a href="https://hacksc.com">HackSC</a>, Southern California's flagship hackathon, where
            I'm on the Hacker Experience team. I primarily work on bringing in amazing speakers and selecting cool prizes,
            but I also chip in on the engineering team from time to time so we can revolutionize the hackathon experience
            together. I also copy edit for the <a href="https://dailytrojan.com">Daily Trojan</a> and <a
              href="https://www.uscannenbergmedia.com/"> Annenberg Media</a>, where I can fulfill my commitment to accurate,
            high-quality journalism.</p>
          <p>In my (rare) spare time, you can find me eating Taiwanese food, <a
              href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/7pqZbX1kOheeGjIY5B6i6M">listening to music</a>, or rooting for the
            Washington Nationals. Feel free to reach out; I'd love to chat!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </body>
</PageLayout>
